div.p:
                    f. 1. In summary we envisage GA res along following lines: 

                            a.

Noting with approval terms of armistice agreement;

                            b.

Reaffirming UN objective of a unified, etc. Korea;

                            c.

Appointing a UN rep to represent UN in bringing about this objective;
                            and

                            d.

Reaffirming relief program.
